<div class="quizMenuContainer h-100">
	<div class="card my-1 mx-5 quizCard h-80">
		<div class="btn formBtn returnBtn"><i class="fas fa-chevron-circle-left"></i></div>
		<div class="card-header">
			<div class="card-img-top" style="background-image:url('./data/image/default.dat');"></div>
			<h5 class="card-title quizName" style="background-color:var(--cI)">Quiz Name</h5>
			<h6 class="card-subtitle quizUsername" style="color:var(--cI)">by Username</h6>
		</div>
		<div class="card-body my-1 mx-3">
			<p class="quizDesc">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Ut sodales feugiat rhoncus. In efficitur velit eget dui facilisis, eget varius dolor viverra. Proin sollicitudin id enim quis varius. Proin at eros quis eros malesuada efficitur. Sed vestibulum velit ut elit consectetur condimentum. In sagittis tempor turpis eget fringilla. Sed tempus sem eu dui pharetra, sed gravida metus fringilla. Suspendisse rutrum tempus lobortis.</p>
		</div>
		<hr>
		<div class="card-tags quizTags mx-3 p-1 h-20">
			<span class="card-tag"><i class="fab fa-slack-hash"></i>hashtag</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="quizMenuControl my-4 mx-5 p-1 h-10">
		<div class="btn formBtn quizMenuBtn mx-0" id="quizMenuPlay">
			<i class="fas fa-play mx-2"></i><span class="quizBtnText font-xs-100 font-md-0">Play</span>
		</div>
		<div class="btn formBtn quizMenuBtn mx-0" id="quizMenuEdit">
			<i class="fas fa-pen-square mx-2"></i><span class="quizBtnText font-xs-100 font-md-0">Edit</span>
		</div>
		<div class="btn formBtn quizMenuBtn mx-0" id="quizMenuDelete">
			<i class="fas fa-trash mx-2"></i><span class="quizBtnText font-xs-100 font-md-0">Delete</span>
		</div>
		<div class="btn formBtn quizMenuBtn mx-0" id="quizMenuSave">
			<i class="fas fa-bookmark mx-2"></i><span class="quizBtnText font-xs-100 font-md-0">Save to List</span>
		</div>
		<div class="btn formBtn quizMenuBtn mx-0" id="quizMenuPreview">
			<i class="fas fa-play-circle mx-2"></i><span class="quizBtnText font-xs-100 font-md-0">Preview Song</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>